text: Jacek Krukowski (born 25 August 1969) is a Polish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Poland Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Kwidzyn
